---
title: Spiced Chicken Quinoa Bowl with Roasted Rainbow Veggies & Lemon-Chive Aioli
description: The secret to an amazing quinoa bowl? Add roasted rainbow veggies for hearty flavour, mildly spiced chicken breast, creamy aioli and a nutty garnish for texture. Mix together for a truly magical result!
